{"tid":1897443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛指中國前所未有嚴格應對疫情","createTime":"2020-02-25T17:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T17:59:21.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f4927fb52ee27ccc8d57423c6ff1e25227c77a17","tid":1897443,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:34:01.000Z","msg":"世衛指中國前所未有嚴格應對疫情<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織專家組早前到中國調查新型冠狀病毒，指確診病例在全球各地急速蔓延，需要超快速應對疫情大流行。官員指調查後，一致評價中國以前所未有的嚴格及創新方式應對疫情，並改變了疫情爆發的過程，認為疫情已停止迅速上升，下降速度亦超過預期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1268033&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1268033%26csid%3D261_367&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=49e82d6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1268033&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"f6286cc4942588eade20dd5f7fdbfe74830c5a0d","tid":1897443,"uid":268519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"講完有冇笑"},{"pid":"7ac50eb2066e6d6cb38412e24af520feab65cb44","tid":1897443,"uid":240648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:36:47.000Z","msg":"點先可以做到講完笑但自己唔笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶到咁撚出面 改名叫支衛啦"},{"pid":"66a942f65a77b9ad33334d67c4bb6ed2a69afb89","tid":1897443,"uid":65556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幾好聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ob6s0qjjKhY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOb6s0qjjKhY&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=66bd3f96\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ob6s0qjjKhY</a><br />\n\t</span>"},{"pid":"5b7f8dbf674200a7e0fcfdfca2879b485d4c05b6","tid":1897443,"uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:39:24.00